layerDefinition.name: OpenStreetMap Labels
layerDefinition.description: daylight v1.54, builder v1.18 | This 3D base layer presents labels of OpenStreetMap (OSM) data hosted by Esri. Esri created this 3D base layer of labels from the Daylight map distribution of OSM data, which is supported by Meta. The 3D base layer trees will be updated every month with the latest version of OSM Daylight data.
